&lt;p&gt;The Director will act as the operational product leader for the portfolio—owning execution rigor, coaching Product Managers, managing cross-functional alignment, and ensuring that the R&amp;amp;D teams deliver consistent, high-quality outcomes. This is a player–coach role that requires deep engagement with teams, customers, and stakeholders on a daily basis.&lt;/p&gt;
